queries.sql: SELECT `c`.*, CONCAT(ea.first_name, " ", `ea`.`second_name`, " ", `ea`.`last_name`, " ", ea.second_last_name) author, `ea`.`user_id`, `u`.`profile_picture`, CONCAT(er.first_name, " ", `er`.`second_name`, " ", `er`.`last_name`, " ", er.second_last_name) responsible, `ca`.`category`, `cs`.`status`, `ct`.`type` FROM `complaints` `c` LEFT JOIN `employees` `ea` ON `ea`.`user_id` = `c`.`created_by` LEFT JOIN `users` `u` ON `u`.`user_id` = `ea`.`user_id` LEFT JOIN `employees` `er` ON `er`.`user_id` = `c`.`user_id` LEFT JOIN `categories` `ca` ON `ca`.`category_id` = `c`.`category_id` LEFT JOIN `complaints_status` `cs` ON `cs`.`complaint_status_id` = `c`.`complaint_status_id` LEFT JOIN `complaints_types` `ct` ON `ct`.`complaint_type_id` = `c`.`complaint_type_id` WHERE `c`.`deleted_at` IS NULL AND `c`.`user_id` = '1'
